# Admin Section Layout Consistency

For Admin tabs, follow `view-architecture-pattern.mdc` defaults first.

Admin-specific additions:

- Keep top-level tab containers on shared section shells (`detail-section` + `ui-panel-section`).
- Prefer established Admin subsection cards/classes already used in the feature.
- Reuse existing table/form wrappers before introducing new Admin-only layout classes.
